$ System.Reflection (namespace)
@ System.Reflection

The `System.Reflection` namespace contains types that provide information about → Microsoft/dot-net/assembly[assemblies], modules, members, parameters etc.

Reflection is possible because the underlying code is → Microsoft/dot-net/managed-code[managed].

sa:
  → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Reflection/reflect_ps1[`reflect.ps1`] is a → Windows/PowerShell/script[PowerShell script]to reflect → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes[.NET types].
